commit.message: Trying solution from pytest-dev/pytest/issues/4770 to fix build issues on appveyor.
Attempt to fix issue reported by Codacy (backed by pylint?)
Register mark with pytest

Add failing tests for duration fix

The duration fix:

    ignore.append('_pytest')

seems to prevent freezegun from freezing `time`.

This adds two tests and creates a fixture variant of the duration test:

* `test_marker_durations` - original test for fix, test passes because
  fix is applied
* `test_fixture_durations` - same test but with a fixture; fails because
  the fix is not applied
* `test_fixture_freezes_time` - fixture freezes time successfully,
  because the fix seems to break `time`
* `test_marker_freezes_time` - marker does not freeze time; fails
  because the fix is applied
